# ── Compiled Rust static libraries ───────────────────────────────────────────
# These are built locally by running build_crypto_lib.sh before development.
# Never commit — they are large, architecture-specific, and must always
# match the current construct-core source.
libconstruct_core.a
libconstruct_core_mac.a
libconstruct_core_sim.a
ConstructCore.xcframework/**/*.a

